    "body": "The 2300 gas limit for the fallback function only applies when it is called via `transfer` or `send`. If you send ether to the contract in any other way, the fallback function can have more than 2300 gas. More info at http://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/v0.4.21/contracts.html#fallback-function",
