    "body": "Worst case: 2300 gas for fallback function. Best case: more than 2300 gas for fallback function. But don't take my word for it. Just try it:\r\n\r\n* Open https://remix.ethereum.org\r\n* Paste this contract in there: https://gist.github.com/redsquirrel/6f4b7a2efbeebe6f2df78aad1cb1853e\r\n* Click the Run tab, Choose JavaScript VM for Environment, click Create to deploy the contract\r\n* Click (fallback)\r\n* In the output area at the bottom, click Details\r\n* You'll notice the execution cost was 112,267, which is a lot more than 2300.\r\n",
